## 🛠 Excel Skills Used
- PivotTables for KPI calculations  
- Slicers for dynamic filtering (Region, Category, Year)  
- KPI cards for headline metrics  
- Charts for revenue trends and product analysis  
- Sheet protection for data integrity  

