## 📑 Ecommerce Dataset
The dataset contains **5,000+ rows** of transactions with the following fields:  
- 🆔 Order ID  
- 📅 Order Date  
- 👤 Customer Name  
- 🌍 Region & City  
- 🛒 Category & Sub‑Category  
- 📦 Product Name  
- 🔢 Quantity  
- 💰 Unit Price, Sales, Profit  
- 🎟️ Discount  
- 💳 Payment Mode  
- 📆 Month & Year  

